Kristalina Georgieva, Managing Director, International Monetary Fund, Valdis Dombrovskis, Commissioner, European Commission, Madis Müller, Governor, Eesti Pank and Klemen Boštjančič, Minister, Ministry of Finance, Slovenia with the moderator Ali Aslan discussed how to preserve fiscal sustainability and resilience to shocks, especially in the context of limited fiscal space and growing financing needs related to climate and security policies.